#: views/admin-settings.php:149
msgid "Border thickness around each emoji to create visual separation."
msgstr "每個表情符號周圍都有加粗的邊框，以創造視覺上的分隔感。"

#: views/admin-settings.php:240
msgid ""
"Changing or disabling reactions will not affect existing reactions in the "
"database. They will simply not be displayed."
msgstr "更改或停用反應不會影響資料庫中已有的反應。它們只會不再顯示。"

#: views/admin-settings.php:94
msgid ""
"Choose which emoji to use for comment reactions (replaces the default heart)."
msgstr "選擇用於評論反應的表情符號（替換預設的愛心）。"

#: views/admin-settings.php:72
msgid "Comment Reaction Emoji"
msgstr "評論表情符號"

#: views/admin-settings.php:160
msgid ""
"Configure the available reaction types. Drag to reorder, toggle to "
"enable/disable."
msgstr "設定可用的反應類型。拖曳即可重新排序，切換即可啟用/停用。"

#: views/admin-settings.php:101
msgid "Counter Display Emojis"
msgstr "櫃檯展示表情符號"

#: views/admin-settings.php:124
msgid "Emoji Overlap"
msgstr "表情符號重疊"

#: views/admin-settings.php:140
msgid "Emoji Stroke"
msgstr "表情符號描邊"

#: views/admin-settings.php:57
msgid "Enable Comment Reactions"
msgstr "啟用評論反應"

#: views/admin-settings.php:42
msgid "Enable Multi-Reactions"
msgstr "啟用多重反應"

#: views/admin-settings.php:62
msgid "Enable reaction functionality on comments"
msgstr "啟用評論的回覆功能"

#. Description of the plugin
msgid ""
"Enhanced reaction system with multiple reaction types (like, love, laugh, "
"wow, sad, angry) for Fluent Community posts and comments. Replace the "
"default heart reaction with a dropdown picker featuring six emoji reactions."
msgstr ""
"Fluent Community "
"的貼文和評論新增了增強型表情系統，支援多種表情類型（按讚、喜歡、笑、哇、難過、生氣）。預設的心形表情被替換為包含六個表情符號的下拉選擇器。"

#: includes/class-reactions-api.php:898
msgid "Failed to update reaction type."
msgstr "反應類型更新失敗。"

