#: views/admin-settings.php:50
msgid ""
"When enabled, the default Fluent Community heart reaction will be replaced "
"with multiple reaction options."
msgstr "啟用後，Fluent Community 的預設心形表情將會被多個表情選項取代。"

#: views/admin-settings.php:65
msgid ""
"When enabled, users can react to comments with multiple emoji options. If "
"disabled, comments will use the default Fluent Community reaction system."
msgstr "啟用此功能後，使用者可以使用多種表情符號選項回應評論。如果停用此功能，則評論將使用 Fluent Community 的預設回覆系統。"

